text: Jeremy Charles Hallett (born 18 October 1970) played first-class and List A cricket for Somerset between 1990 and 1995 and for the Combined Universities cricket team between 1991 and 1994. He was born at Yeovil, Somerset. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:English cricketers Category:Somerset cricketers Category:People educated at Millfield Category:British Universities cricketers
